flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Scheduled global planning cadence (weekly/monthly) or major event (new model launch, market shock) that requires SKU/configuration-level forecast refresh and production alignment.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest transactional, master and market data into the analytics foundation]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast + RCA Service - Produce SKU/configuration-level forecasts and diagnostic signals]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder + Remote Functions + CWB Lifecycle - Orchestrate constrained mix optimization and generate CWB recommendations}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: UI Screens (CWB) + CWB Lifecycle - Planner review and approval with override capability]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions + Process Builder + Notification - Write approved production and allocation plans back to ERP and notify stakeholders]
  N5 --> N6[UI: Subject Areas + UI Screens (dashboard) - Surface KPIs and monitor model performance]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Higher forecast accuracy and mix alignment at launch, reduced inventory tied to forecast error, improved production efficiency and COGS through optimized configuration mix and capacity-aware allocations.]
  N3 -->|Forecast uncertainty or model confide...| B1[Process Builder triggers scenario analysis and conservative ramp proposals; create CWB exception for cross-functional launch review]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Stakeholders select phased ramp or conservative allocation; system records approved ramp and updates plans]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Optimization yields infeasible alloca...| B2[Remote Functions mark infeasible allocations and Process Builder invokes prioritized reallocation rules (profitability-first) and routes to planners via CWB]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Mix is rebalanced toward feasible, higher-margin configurations; production plan updated and notified]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Large divergence between recommended ...| B3[Raise an exception that requires manual override and legal/contract review before writeback]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Writeback is blocked until exception is resolved; audit trail captured and stakeholders notified]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]